WEREWOLVES AND WANDERERS
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------


THIS GAME IS A REMAKE OF THE (POPULAR) GAMES WEREWOLVES AND WANDERERS,
MADE WITH FLASK(PYTHON) AND SINATRA(RUBY), TO BE MICROSERVICE-BASED.

THIS GAME IS PLAYED BY RUNNNING ALL THE SERVERS IN SNAKES AND GEMS FOLDERS AND THEN THE CLIENT.

VERIFY THAT THE METHOD game(), IN THE ONLY CLIENT IS BEING RAN.

ENJOY, YOU SHOULD PLAY WITH CAPS LOCKED (HENCE WHY THIS README IS WRITTEN LIKE THIS).
